01

The confirmed case load is still being digested

The 21st, January twenty-eight. Saturday. Fine. Another week went by.

A total of 397 new cases and 109 new deaths (106 in Hubei) were reported nationwide on May 21.

As of the 21st, there were 53,284 confirmed cases (including 11,477 serious cases) , 20,659 cured cases, 2,345 dead cases, 76,288 confirmed cases and 5,365 suspected cases.

There were 366 newly confirmed cases in Hubei (314 in Wuhan) , 1767 newly cured cases (992 in Wuhan) , 106 newly dead cases (90 in Wuhan) , 47,647 currently confirmed cases (36,680 in Wuhan) , among which 10,892 were serious cases (9,555 in Wuhan) .

There were 2,250 cumulative deaths (1,774 in Wuhan) and 63,454 confirmed cases (45,660 in Wuhan) . There were 1125 new suspected cases (927 in Wuhan) and 4490 suspected cases (3414 in Wuhan) .

Hubei Province added back the number of cases that had been verified on the 19th and corrected for the number of new cases on the same day. Accordingly, on 19 February, the number of newly diagnosed cases nationwide was revised to 820, the cumulative number of newly diagnosed cases nationwide was revised to 75,002, and the cumulative number of discharged cases nationwide was revised to 16,157. On the 20th, the cumulative number of confirmed cases nationwide was revised to 75,891, and the cumulative number of discharged cases nationwide was revised to 18,266.

02

It's been a bit of a mess these last couple of days

A total of 349 new confirmed cases were reported at 7:00 am on the 20th (615 in Wuhan, 13 in Xiantao and 10 other cities in Jingmen and Xianning) .

Although the decline was significant (1,933 on the 16th, 1,807 on the 17th and 1,693 on the 18th) . But, you know, people don't understand.

Where did 266 people go?

On My wechat account, there are waves of skepticism.

@ EMINAMI: YOU'RE A statistician. In Hubei, this kind of statistical game can not be avoided. The number of diagnoses today can not be reduced by the number of emission reductions after being diagnosed in the past. Otherwise, there will be a situation where the number of diagnoses in the past has been overreported for many reasons, but the number of diagnoses in the future will be daily and more serious, but it's always offset, zero for the day, zero for the carry-over, zero for the carry-over until it's zero. Reductions should be made from the current number of diagnoses and can not be made from new additions or reductions on the same day.

I happen to be in charge of social science statistics at the Bureau of Statistics, including the National Bureau of Statistics of the People's Republic of China Department.

Now, it turns out, these netizens have the same idea as the new provincial Party secretary.

Fortunately, at 10:40 a.m. , the Hubei Provincial Health and Health Commission's response came.

The reason is that on the 18th, the National Health and Health Commission issued the notice on Printing and distributing the sixth edition of the COVID-19's diagnosis and treatment plan, and the category of clinical cases unique to Hubei province was cancelled compared with the fifth edition of the diagnosis and treatment plan, only confirmed and suspected cases will be retained.

As a result, the number of people in Wuhan remained the same, the number of people in other cities and states decreased, the number of the province decreased.

The fact that it's nearly four hours late gives you an idea of what's really going on. We're GONNA have to talk more.

One thing led to another.

A total of 411 new cases of coronary pneumonia were reported in the province on the 20th, including 319 cases in Wuhan.

The number of new cases is up a bit from yesterday. However, the "unfortunate" news came more than 12:00 p.m. , with 631 new confirmed cases in Hubei (319 in Wuhan) .

More than an hour later, the Hubei Provincial Health and Health Commission made an explanation: Prisons in our province did not have access to the network reporting system for infectious diseases. After receiving the manual report card from the Prison Department on the night of February 20, after careful examination and confirmation, as at 2400 hours on February 20, of the 271 confirmed cases of NCP reported by the prison authorities, 51 cases were previously included in the relevant regional statistics and published, while the remaining 220 confirmed cases and 10 suspected cases are now included in the 20 February epidemic data for publication.

There were 271 confirmed cases in Hubei prison system, including 230 in Wuhan Women's prison and 41 in Shayang Hanjin prison, all of which were imported cases.

More than 400 cases have been confirmed in prisons across the country. You don't have to deal with the warden or anyone else.

Tu Yuanchao, deputy director of the Hubei Provincial Health and Health Commission, said at a press conference on the prevention and control of the Hubei epidemic at 4:00 p.m. on the 21st that the adjustment of the new pneumonia data released by Hubei Province, especially Wuhan, these days has aroused high social concern. In this regard, provincial Party Secretary Ying Yong attaches great importance to the clear demand for the confirmed cases not to be allowed to reduce the nuclear, the nuclear reduction must be added back in full, to the relevant responsible people to find out the facts, serious accountability.

This means that confirmed cases should be retained in accordance with the requirements of the fifth edition, rather than simply being revised for other diseases or classified as suspected cases in accordance with the sixth edition criteria. In that case, there may be a new wrinkle. The secretary's concern is that. In the spirit of a responsible attitude for the people, the issue of a point to consider, rather believe that it is also a relatively safe approach. Wuhan and Hubei can no longer afford to relax.

Feb. 21,23:23, Hubei announced that it would add the February 19 nuclear reduction data back to confirmed cases, revising the number of new confirmed cases from 349 to 775, Huanqiu. COM reported.

It's called correcting your mistakes, correcting them quickly, and correcting them easily.

03

Progress has been made in stages

A meeting of the Politburo of the Communist Party of China was held on the 21st to study the prevention and control of the new coronavirus epidemic, and to plan and coordinate the prevention and control of the epidemic as well as economic and social development.

The meeting stressed that the current epidemic spread of the initial containment, prevention and control work achieved phased results. At the same time, we should be clear that the turning point of the national epidemic development has not yet arrived, the situation in Hubei Province and Wuhan is still grim and complex.

"effective" is also a phase, the key is that we have not yet come to replace the inflection point. This valuable insight, hopefully, will emerge in the second half of February.

Epidemic Prevention and control and economic and social development should take a proportion.

What is the general situation? The relevant data can reflect.

China's top 500 manufacturers have returned 97 percent of their output and nearly 60 percent of their output, according to the Capacity utilization. Among the enterprises that have resumed work and production, the average rate of employees arriving at work is 66.17% , the average rate of members'enterprises starting work is 75.24% , and the average rate of Capacity utilization is 58.98% .

In general, the state-owned enterprises are better than the private enterprises in resuming work and production.

Therefore, the place that can resume production overcomes difficulty to resume production as soon as possible, this is the biggest support that fights epidemic disease.

Recently, the relevant departments issued a number of preferential policies, combing is necessary.

04

We're GONNA have to fight one siege after another

Ying Yong, the party secretary of Hubei Province, chaired a video dispatching meeting on the prevention and control of the epidemic on Thursday.

Ying Yong once again stressed that the epidemic prevention and control into an orderly track, the epidemic situation is still very serious:

 The patient base is still large, and the task of treatment is daunting

 weaknesses in screening screening and diversion

 The number of people with latent infections is unknown

 The good foundation is not yet solid.

Ying Yong stresses the "six imperatives" :

 To carry out large-scale Split Second screening around the two key links of treatment and isolation, so as to identify "acceleration" , achieve full coverage of admission, early intervention in treatment and strict management of patients with fever, truly realize should be separated, should be collected, should check check, should rule rule;

 We should focus on the important window period when sister provinces and municipalities provide support to Hubei province through their counterparts. We should make every effort to effectively carry out the work of diversion and isolation, promote the formation of closed loops for data and information, and for admission and treatment, so as to ensure that the bottom numbers are clear, personnel are accurate and data are authentic, ensure close contacts are isolated in a timely manner to prevent latent infections from becoming a source of mobile transmission;

 To create the conditions for converting the existing isolation points into isolation treatment centres, equipped with medical force and endowed with treatment functions, those with the conditions can be directly converted into hospitals, truly moving the treatment threshold forward;

 The work of screening and screening shall be completed, and the patients shall be transferred to medical treatment and discharged from hospital, so as to help them pass through the period of isolation

 emphasis should be placed on both severe and mild care to minimize the transition from mild to severe illness;

 keeping a good balance between the treatment of NCP and the urgent need for medical services in the community, so as to avoid the risk of one losing sight of the other.

It's a good recovery from the issues we all care about. The thinking is clear.

Since the outbreak, Wuhan or tens of thousands of families are suffering from new pneumonia secondary disasters. They are cancer patients in need of chemotherapy, uremia patients in need of dialysis, heart attack patients in need of surgery... unable to guarantee immediate treatment, and for them a threat of death, even faster than the new coronary pneumonia.

On February 16, Wuhan Health Commission announced the partial admission of patients with non-new coronary pneumonia to meet the medical needs of patients with chronic severe illness, pregnant women, children, hemodialysis patients.

However, some non-ncp patients lost their lives while waiting. Zhang Qin, a nurse in Wuchang, Wuhan, lost her father because he could not maintain dialysis, the Xiaoxiang Morning Post reported on Jan. 31. "Father, I am saving others, for you I have no way, go well, I love you, Dad. " This is Zhang Qin's final confession to his father.

On the afternoon of Feb. 17, hundreds of cancer and diabetes patients waited in line outside a designated pharmacy in Hankou. In the volunteer organization's help group, the leukemia and so on non-new coronary pneumonia patient's help message one after another.

This feeling, a bit like the first 10 days of the epidemic, there is no bed helpless feeling.

The new secretary stressed this point, which is crucial.

05

NUCLEIC ACID test stock cleared to zero

On the morning of the 21st, the joint prevention and Control Mechanism of the State Council held a press conference, or some good news.

For example, four down, one up, some provinces zero report.

The vaccine is expected to be declared for clinical trials as soon as late April. Two more months.

At present, five technical routes to speed up the development of vaccines, some projects have already entered the animal testing stage.

In terms of medicine and clinical treatment, TCM has achieved positive results in blocking the development of light to heavy patients, and now it seems to be working very well.

Traditional Chinese medicine treatment is the focus of the recent debate on Wechat. I often receive prescriptions from the old Chinese doctor.

Plasma therapy was incorporated into the fifth edition of the diagnostic protocol and further refined in the sixth edition.

Recently, the nation's first plasma treatment of patients from the first district of Jiangxia People's Hospital (Concord Jiangnan Hospital) discharged. After receiving "plasma therapy" treatment, several patients are gradually recovering.

Liu Bende, deputy director of the First People's Hospital in Jiangxia District, the initiator of plasma therapy for new coronary pneumonia, said he proposed and worked with a number of units to start plasma therapy for new coronary pneumonia with the simple aim of saving more people.

Liu Bende was also a first-line doctor in SARS 17 years ago. When SARS was also tried to use convalescent serum for treatment, some experts were very brave to use convalescent blood for clinical treatment after rough preparation, really effective.

At the end of January, Liu Bende, as a project declarant, submitted the emergency science and Technology Project Declaration form to Hubei Provincial Science and technology department in the form of joint declaration. The declared items are highly valued, and are suggested to be implemented while declaring.

The most important and happy news on the 21st was that the nucleic acid test had been zeroed out. It wasn't easy.

Previously, Wuhan required the "four categories of people" nucleic acid testing stock "continue to intensify, as soon as possible clear zero. ".

Wuhan, 17-20,4 days in time to promote screening screening screening screening, "four categories of personnel" nucleic acid detection "great speed. 42,515 person-times nucleic acid detection.

Starting from the 22nd, a new day is added to the day to clear the zero. This should also be a small inflection point. So far, 40 relevant institutions in Wuhan have carried out new coronavirus nucleic acid detection, the average detection capacity of 20,000 people.

Florida test -- entering the hospital -- no more holds up.

Ten days ago, Fangxian, Shiyan City, offered a reward of 1,000 yuan for the discovery of fever patients. Later, Huanggang followed suit, and now Hanyang has begun to do the same.

In the early morning of the 21st, the new Hanyang District Hanyang District Hanyang District Hanyang District Hanyang District Hanyang District Hanyang District new pneumonia control and Prevention Headquarters issued a notice to ensure that no one was left behind in the investigation of new coronavirus infection in Hanyang District, and decided to implement an aggressive new Hanyang District new pneumonia prevention and control self-investigation incentive scheme.

All at home to declare and first confirmed as fever patients and to receive centralized isolation, NUCLEIC ACID testing, after verification, each person to give 200 yuan reward;

Those who declare voluntarily at home and are suspected of being infected for the first time and receive centralized isolation and nucleic acid testing will be awarded 300 yuan per person;

Those who declare voluntarily at home and are first confirmed to be infected with the new coronavirus will be awarded 500 yuan per person.

It's the only way.

Jiang'an District has taken the same approach.

After a month of lockdown, the hospital was finally back to normal, and the number of outpatients dropped. This is the result of the efforts of the whole nation for a month.

Take the fever clinic of Wuhan Seven Hospital as an example. You can see the terrible numbers of the past.

On January 24th there were more than 1,300 outpatient visits, and since then they have remained roughly between 800 and 1,000.

On February 20th, there were 119 visits, and the number of people coming to see me has changed a lot.

Between 8:00 a.m. and 12:04 a.m. on the 21st, 69 citizens were checked in.

The less, the better.

Wuhan plans to build 19 more shelter hospitals, with 30,000 shelter hospital beds to be stocked in Wuhan by February 25, Hu Yabo, Wuhan's executive vice mayor, said at a news conference on February 21.

Currently, 13 shelter hospitals in Wuhan have opened their cabins, 13,348 beds are available for treatment, and 9,313 beds have been used, and already has 72 support to assist Wuhan medical team into the Shelter Hospital.

How's the Shelter Hospital? It's a particular concern of the staycation.

Mcdull's "7 days of my life in Lake Tazi shelter" was a hit on the Internet.

The daily flow chart of the Shelter Hospital in this article is very intuitionistic and worth seeing.

06

Foreign aid is over 35,000

Nearly 4,500 health care workers from Inner Mongolia, Jiangsu, Gansu, Heilongjiang, Yunnan, Ningxia, Shandong, Fujian, Shanghai, Sichuan, Hebei, Guangxi, Hainan and Jilin, went to all over Hubei City Medical Unit to carry out the patient rescue work.

These support Hubei medical teams from the medical units of breathing, serious disease, medicine, infection, nursing, testing and other professional, they will complete the docking with the counterpart hospital to carry out patient care.

As of the 21st, Wuhan Tianhe Airport has welcomed 34,500 medical and nursing personnel from Hubei Province, guaranteeing the transportation of more than 5000 tons of epidemic prevention materials.

The actual number must be more than 34,500, because there are also high-speed trains and buses.

Some of these contrarians have been here almost a month. Their feelings can best illustrate the changes in Wuhan this month.

People in Wuhan may be especially touched by a diary published on the popular account of the Central Government's wechat account.

On the first day of the Lunar New Year from Hangzhou, Yu Chengbo, a member of the Democratic Progressive Party, chief of the medical team of Zhejiang's first aid team to Hubei Province and chief physician of the Infection Department of the First Affiliated Hospital of Zhejiang University Medical College, has been in Wuhan for more than 20 days.

In his diary, he said that the patient is well, is the most gratifying thing; watching the death of life, secretly tears at night.

At the end of his diary, he wrote:

Now Wuhan is not as lonely as when we first came, she is slowly recovering vitality, with a "spring" atmosphere. Although there are still many seriously ill and critically ill patients, many of whom can not be transferred to better hospitals in time, medical personnel from all over the country are coming to Wuhan one after another with medical equipment and protective materials; From the hospital staff responsible for docking more serious infection, staff shortage, to now can function properly; from the number of nucleic acid tests too small, to now is fully enough..

I believe that one day, as usual, the bustling Wuhan can see us with the joy of victory, the result of the mission safely home. This Day, I think it's coming.

The most talked about name these two days is "Doctor Peng" .

On the evening of the 20th, 30-year-old Doctor Peng Yinhua of the People's Hospital of Jiangxia District / Xiehe Jiangnan Hospital was killed in a fierce battle with new coronary pneumonia. The white-clad Warrior has been getting a marriage license for more than two years, but will never be able to attend his postponed wedding, leaving his heavily pregnant wife behind.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
He gave not only his skill, but his life.

Care for the medical staff is a must.

On the 21st, Wuhan made it clear that front-line medical staff should have at least two days'rest for 10 days, a meal standard of 200 yuan per person per day, and a one-off consolation grant of 6,000 yuan per person. Those who are not active, active and evasive in the work of the medical team supporting the Han people in the service guarantee, and who affect the prevention and control of the epidemic and cause adverse effects, will be seriously held accountable according to the rules and regulations.

07

Accountability

Provincial and municipal party secretaries are busy treating and quarantining people. What's deputy chief Chen doing? Accountability.

In the face of major tests, we can test our cadres even more. Chen Yixin, deputy head of the Central Steering Group and Secretary General of the Central Political and Legal Affairs Commission, is in Wuhan to oversee the implementation of incentives and accountability in the prevention and control of the epidemic. He stressed that the Battle of Wuhan, grasp to inspire the real, grasp accountability, excellent line of fire promotion, unqualified prompt accountability, to promote cadres to take on, as, dedication spirit.

As of February 21, Wuhan has promoted 20 cadres and 34 members of the Party for fire-line development; Discipline Inspection and supervision authorities have investigated and dealt with 385 problems, dealt with 620 people in terms of accountability, 6 cadres at the bureau level and 127 at the department level.

Their mistakes fall into two broad categories:

The first category is the violation of epidemic prevention and control work discipline issues. Only one street in Xima Street, Jiang'an District, has been held accountable for three people: Chen Qiuhua, secretary of the sub-district Party Work Committee, who failed to carry out the measures of the closed management of the sub-district. He failed to attend the site inspection and dispatch of the closed management of the sub-district, on the part of the closed management of materials, personnel insufficient grasp of the 73 areas under the jurisdiction of the implementation of closed management do not understand; Tan Shuhan, deputy director of the street, and Xiong Lin, a researcher of the fourth level, failed to coordinate and solve the practical problems of contacting their counterparts in the community in a timely manner, resulting in eight residential areas having problems such as unattended entrances and exits, unattended body temperature measurements, and residents entering and leaving at will. All three have been put on file for review by Party discipline.

The second kind is the Cadre Sinks the Cadre Work Style not to be true and so on. Tang Jianxin, an agricultural and rural bureau official in Wuhan, visited the community only three times during the administration of the sinking, working only about two hours at a time and being investigated by the Party.

Yesterday, Ezhou responded to the problem of rotting cabbages in Guizhou after 28 hours of long-distance transport. However, there was no answer to the police station to divide the food and fruit.

On the night of the 21st, the Ezhou Commission for Discipline Inspection and supervision issued opinions on the illegal distribution and collection of donated living materials from Fenghuang Street and Fenghuang Police Station in the Echeng district.

After investigation, Yu Jianbing, secretary of the Party Work Committee of Fenghuang Street in Echeng District, Ezhou, and commander of Fenghuang Street Epidemic Prevention and Control Headquarters, improperly performed his duties and violated the regulations on the distribution and management of donated living materials for epidemic prevention and control, without authorization, the scope and standards of distribution shall be expanded, and donations of living materials shall be distributed and received in violation of regulations. Du Huanbao, Secretary of the Leading Party Group and Director of the Bureau for Development, reform and economic information of Echeng District, improperly performed his duties in charge of the distribution and distribution of donated materials in the city of Hubei, in violation of the regulations on the distribution and management of donated living materials for epidemic prevention and control, without authorization, he decided to allocate the relevant materials to the Phoenix police station. Cheng Xuejun, director of the Phoenix Police Station of the Echeng District branch of the Ezhou Public Security Bureau, allocates donated living materials from the streets of Phoenix to the officers and staff of the station.

Yu Jianbing, Du Huanbao Party discipline on file, supervision on file, and be removed from office. Cheng Xuejun was suspended by the Municipal Public Security Bureau, and further investigations into the relevant issues continued.

There are masks in front of the city, "shouted at" by provincial-level authorities, and fruits and vegetables in Ezhou. These are all lessons that public officials should learn.

What about the people? How do you deal with profit? This is the first lesson of public service.

The general secretary learned how to treat his peasant brothers in Liangjiahe village. They are advised to take a good look at Xi Jinping's seven years of educated youth.
